2000-06-03  Mo DeJong  <mdejong@redhat.com>

	* Makefile.in: Merged from unix/Makefile.in
	* aclocal.m4:
	* autogen.sh: Added
	* configure: Added
	* configure.in: Merged from unix/configure.in
